parameters:
\F[ajiri_angry2]Yui: "Honestly, I've never beaten Sirius even once in
training... I wonder how far I can go against that child..."

\F[ajiri_angry2]Yui: "Well, there's no use thinking about it. All I can do
now is give it my best."

\F[furi_smile]Akane: "I found it! AkeLUNAR!! Hehe♪ No need for a Codename
anymore! I'm nobody! I can be free from everything♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_angry2]\AA[2]Yui: "Even though you weren't completely dissatisfied with
the title of the strongest agent. Well, fine. I have no
intention of playing your supporting role any longer."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_angry2]\AA[2]Yui: "Prepare yourself. I'll make you show your true colors!
Sirius!!"

\F[sumire_trouble]Sumire: "Kikyo-san said that in the kingdom, becoming naked
is the rule... And so I ended up throwing away my bracelet
too..."

\F[sumire_trouble]Sumire: "I can't fight if I can't transform... Ah... Oh,
excuse me for interrupting! But... I can't overlook this."

\F[sumire_angry]Sumire: "I'll find the weakness of Akane Suzaku who has
turned into a monster!"

\FF[ajiri_shadow]Yui: "The Burst Ball isn't effective at all! Could it be...
Sirius is also the strongest as a Poison!?"
\FF[ajiri_shadow]Yui: "Then... is there no chance for us to win...?"
\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_shadow]\AA[1]Akane: "Win? Against whom...? Do we really need to...?"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_shadow]\AA[2]Yui: "What are you saying...! If we don't win... the world
will be free to..."
\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_shadow]\AA[1]Akane: "Isn't that better? No one will be unhappy then♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_shadow]\AA[2]Yui: "That's right... I... why didn't I realize such a
simple thing♪"

\FF[ajiri_free]Yui: "Ufufu♪ Freedom is definitely better, isn't it♪ We
don't need a Condom♪ Our name is just one"

\FF[ajiri_free]Yui: "Everyone... Sirius and Akerunaru... we're all
Freedom♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_free]\AA[1]Akane: "Freedom... That's a good name♪ Ahaha! You've got
taste!"
\F[furi_smile]\FF[ajiri_free]\AA[2]Yui: "Freedom! Freedom♪ Both I and Master... we're Freedom♪"

parameters:
\FF[sumire_shadow]Sumire: "Wearing such a criminal-like black bar over your
eyes... How can you still see my movements... when you
shouldn't be able to..."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[sumire_shadow]\AA[1]Akane: "As long as you're deceived by appearances, you can't
win, can you? I'm different from that baldie. I can see
everything♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[sumire_shadow]\AA[2]Sumire: "But I won't give up. Even with this power flowing
into me... there must be a weakness..."
\F[furi_smile]\FF[sumire_shadow]\AA[2]Sumire: "No... way? Why...? Ah! I, I understand now..."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[sumire_shadow]\AA[2]Sumire: "So there's true freedom in being released from such
annoying things, right? Aaahn♪ Amazing! There's no such
thing as a weakness... an irreversible fall♪"

\FF[sumire_free]Sumire: "No weaknesses means I can attack without any tricks
and make you my ally, doesn't it? Fufu♪ How wonderful...♪"

\FF[sumire_free]Sumire: "I'll attack you over and over until you understand♪
Ufufufu...♪"
